<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta content="text/html; charset=UTF-8" http-equiv="Content-Type">
  <style>
      body {
          font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
          line-height: 1.5;
          color: #333333;
          max-width: 600px;
          margin: 0 auto;
          padding: 20px;
      }
      .container {
          border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
          border-radius: 5px;
          padding: 25px;
          background-color: #f9f9f9;
      }
      .header {
          text-align: center;
          margin-bottom: 25px;
      }
      .otp-container {
          text-align: center;
          margin: 30px 0;
      }
      .otp-code {
          font-size: 32px;
          font-weight: bold;
          letter-spacing: 5px;
          padding: 15px;
          background-color: #ffffff;
          border: 1px dashed #cccccc;
          border-radius: 5px;
          display: inline-block;
      }
      .footer {
          font-size: 12px;
          text-align: center;
          color: #777777;
          margin-top: 30px;
      }
      .warning {
          color: #d73a49;
          font-weight: bold;
      }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="container">
  <div class="header">
    <h2>Verification Code</h2>
  </div>
  <p>Hello,</p>
  <p>We received a request to verify your account. Please use the following One-Time Password (OTP) to complete your verification.</p>

  <strong><%= @email_address %></strong>

  <div class="otp-container">
    <div class="otp-code"><%= @otp %></div>
  </div>

  <p>
    <span class="warning">Important:</span>
    This verification code will expire in 10 minutes.
  </p>

  <p>If you did not request this code, please disregard this email or contact support if you believe this is an error.</p>

  <p>Thank you,</p>
  <p>Your Application Team</p>

  <div class="footer">
    <p>This is an automated message, please do not reply directly to this email.</p>
    <p>If you need assistance, please contact our support team.</p>
  </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>